flowchart LR
  Seed[Seed tx/address] --> Discovery[Tx Discovery]
  Discovery --> TxSet[Related Tx Set]
  TxSet --> TxAnalyzer[TxAnalyzer Artifact Pull]
  TxAnalyzer --> Artifacts[Trace/Source/Opcode/Selectors]
  Artifacts --> Decode[Deterministic Decode]
  Decode --> Evidence[Structured Evidence]
  Evidence --> Modules[ACL/Safe/FundFlow/Loss Modules]
  Modules --> Findings[Findings]
  Findings --> QA[QA Gates]
  QA --> Report[Report Draft]
  Report --> Review[Human Review]
  Review --> Published[Published Report]
